comments: Jokic (DEN) releases his dribble prior to the dribble handoff.
Shamet (PHX) places his hand on Porter Jr.'s (DEN) body while defending the dribble handoff and removes his hand prior to his upward shooting motion.
Ayton (PHX) brings his hands toward Porter Jr. (DEN) and marginal contact occurs as Ayton (PHX) releases away to roll.
Porter Jr. (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball as he contest Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) rotates over and makes marginal contact to Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) body while defending the shot at the rim.
Craig (PHX) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Bridges' (PHX) path and incidental contact occurs as the pick is set.
Porter Jr. (DEN) commits a take foul on Ayton (PHX).
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) dislodges the ball out of bounds.
Bridges (PHX) establishes himself in Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and delivers illegal contact that affects Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) defensive position.
Bridges (PHX) legally contests Murray's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Craig (PHX) is moving alongside Gordon's (DEN) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Murray (DEN) establishes his left foot as his pivot and lifts it before starting his dribble.
Jokic (DEN) briefly grabs Bridges' (PHX) arm during the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) and Bridges (PHX) come together off-ball and incidental contact occurs.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in Murray's (DEN) path and his legs remain within the frame of his body as contact occurs, which he does not deliver.

The crew communicated with Replay Center to determine whether or not Shamet (PHX) was in the restricted area after an offensive foul was called against Gordon (DEN).  While it was confirmed that Shamet was outside the restricted area, the referees also reviewed whether Shamet was in a legal guarding position (an additional reviewable matter for this replay trigger).  Replay showed Shamet was moving into Gordon's path after he had started his upward motion toward the rim, and the initial call on the floor was therefore overturned and Shamet was assessed a blocking foul
Paul (DEN) commits a take foul on Gordon (DEN).
Bridges (PHX) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN).
Shamet (PHX) gathers the pass on his right foot prior to his shot attempt.
